  <h1>
   Opera GX Preferences
  </h1>
  The Opera GX preferences have the following options:
  <br/><img src="https://gms.magecorn.com/Manual/assets/Images/Setup_And_Version/Platform_Preferences/Opera_GX_Prefs.png"/><br/>
  <ul>
   <li>
    <strong>
     Emscripten SDK location
    </strong>
    : This is the location of the Emscripten SDK, required for YYC builds made for Opera GX. Read
    <a href="https://help.yoyogames.com/hc/en-us/articles/4625548722193">
     Setting Up For Opera GX
    </a>
    for information on setting up the SDK.
   </li>
   <li>
    <strong>
     Default Web Server Port
    </strong>
    : This lets you change the default port for the Opera GX web server. Default value is 51264.
   </li>
   <li>
    <strong>
     Default Web Server Address
    </strong>
    : Here you can change the default web server address for the Opera GX web server.Â Default value is 127.0.0.1.
   </li>
   <li>
    <strong>
     Default Web Server Allowed IPs
    </strong>
    : Here you can add in any allowed IPs for the web server and they will be set as default for all devices added through the Target Manager.
   </li>
  </ul>
 </body>
